      "text": "えっ……？　えーっと……優？　どういうこと？\n突然二年生の教室まで来て……生徒会長になる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…? Um… Yu? What do you mean?\nYou suddenly came to a second-year classroom… and you’re becoming president?",
